	(buffer): Change into pointer to utmp, add libc_freeres_ptr.
	(__getutline): Allocate buffer the first time it is run.
	* malloc/mtrace.c (malloc_trace_buffer): Change into char *.
	(mtrace): Allocate malloc_trace_buffer.
