	when closing a partially-initialized object.

	* elf/dl-load.c (_dl_map_object_from_fd) [! USE_TLS]: Call lose
	instead of _dl_fatal_printf when we see PT_TLS.

	* Makeconfig (CPPFLAGS): Fix last change to use $(libof-$(<F))
	instead of $(libof-$<).

